"FAF6F6\"|10<br/>10\n|align=\"center\" bgcolor=\"FAF6F6\"|Safe\n|-\n|-\n|align=\"center\" bgcolor=\"FAF6F6\"|9<br/><small>Semi-finals</small>\n|align=\"center\" bgcolor=\"FAF6F6\"|Quickstep/ \"Mr. Pinstripe Suit\"<br/>Cha-Cha-Cha/ \"[[Push It (Salt-n-Pepa song)|Push It]]\"\n|align=\"center\" bgcolor=\"FAF6F6\"|10<br/>10\n|align=\"center\" bgcolor=\"FAF6F6\"|10<br/>9\n|align=\"center\" bgcolor=\"FAF6F6\"|10<br/>10\n|align=\"center\" bgcolor=\"FAF6F6\"|Safe\n|-\n|-\n|align=\"center\" bgcolor=\"FAF6F6\"|10<br/><small>Finals</small>\n|align=\"center\" bgcolor=\"FAF6F6\"|Rumba/ \"[[Midnight Train to Georgia]]\"<br/>[[Freestyle dance|Freestyle]]/ \"[[Bust a Move (song)|Bust a Move]]\" <br/> [[Paso Doble]]/ \"[[Carnaval de Paris]]\"\n|align=\"center\" bgcolor=\"FAF6F6\"|9<br/>10<br/>10\n|align=\"center\" bgcolor=\"FAF6F6\"|9<br/>10<br/>10\n|align=\"center\" bgcolor=\"FAF6F6\"|10<br/>10<br/>10\n|align=\"center\" bgcolor=\"FAF6F6\"|'''WON'''\n|-\n|}\n{{clear}}\n\n'''Season 15 \u2013 with Karina Smirnoff'''\n\nIn July 2012, it was announced Ohno would return for the all-star [[Dancing with the Stars (U.S. season 15)|fifteenth season]] for a second chance to win the mirrorball trophy; this time he was paired with Season 13 champion professional [[Karina Smirnoff]].<ref>{{cite news |first=Dahvi |last=Shira |title=Dancing with the Stars All-Star Cast Revealed |date=July 27, 2012 |url=http://www.people.com/people/article/0,,20615549,00.html |work=People |accessdate=August 7, 2012 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120729232716/http://www.people.com/people/article/0,,20615549,00.html |archive-date=July 29, 2012 |url-status=live }}</ref> They were voted off during the ninth week of the competition.\n{|class=\"wikitable\"\n|-  style=\"text-align:center; background:#ccc;\"\n| rowspan=\"2\"|'''Week'''\n| rowspan=\"2\"|'''Dance/Song'''\n| colspan=\"3\"|'''Judges' score'''\n| rowspan=\"2\"|'''Result'''\n|-  style=\"text-align:center; background:#ccc;\"\n|  style=\"width:10%; \"|